<entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4454138263351406668</id><published>2015-08-01T14:52:20.235+08:00</published><updated>2015-08-01T14:52:20.235+08:00</updated><title type='text'>按照辩证唯物主义，凡事都有好坏两面.&#xa;同样的道理，共产党独裁统治人民，这种事也有好的一面。在共产党独...</title><content type='html'>按照辩证唯物主义，凡事都有好坏两面.&lt;br /&gt;同样的道理，共产党独裁统治人民，这种事也有好的一面。在共产党独裁时期，很多人很比以前更没有权利，这时候，你最好能够抓住这个机会提高你贿赂的水平，多学点官商勾结技能，等到共产党独裁时期结束的时候，没准你赚取的财产正好可以派上用场。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8933342885575256521/comments/default/4454138263351406668'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8933342885575256521/comments/default/4454138263351406668'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/01/job-in-economy-decline.html?showComment=1438411940235#c4454138263351406668' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8933342885575256521/comments/default/739739299001712427'/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/01/job-in-economy-decline.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8933342885575256521' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/8933342885575256521' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1663270703"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2015年8月1日 下午2:52:00"/></entry>
